    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>cumin seeds</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, transfer the <strong>toasted cumin seeds</strong> to a large bowl and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1676.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1676.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
