            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once the pineapple slices are nearly done, remove the tray from the oven, then add the <strong>sliced brioche bun[s]</strong>, cut-side up, to the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven and cook for a final 3-4 min or until the bun is warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1676.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1676.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
